title: How to install windows 95 in DosBox (without win95 CD)
description:
Its a semi automatic instalation of windows 95 in dosbox.
Need some user interaction, and to create at the end the links to the program.
I still dont know how to make an msi.
It doesent work like admin, the .bat crash.
So you have to install it to a diferente "Programs Files" folder. I sugest the same folder were is this "installer" or bat helper.
